                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-white/80">
                                <span class="text-white font-medium block">Self-hosted LLMs</span>
                                Ollama, Mistral, Open WebUI integration with PHP
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="bg-purple-600 rounded-full p-1.5 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-white/80">
                                <span class="text-white font-medium block">Chatbot Framework</span>
                                Build real-time GPT chatbots inside your Laravel apps
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="bg-purple-600 rounded-full p-1.5 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-white/80">
                                <span class="text-white font-medium block">Context Management</span>
                                Built-in conversation memory and context-switching
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <div class="bg-purple-600 rounded-full p-1.5 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-white/80">
                                <span class="text-white font-medium block">API-first Design</span>
                                Easy API endpoints for frontend & mobile apps
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Ideal for section -->
                    <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Ideal for:</h3>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                            <span class="bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">AI Startups</span>
                            <span class="bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">SaaS Platforms</span>
                            <span class="bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Agencies</span>
                            <span class="bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Developers</span>
                            <span class="bg-white/10 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Educational Apps</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Developer note -->
                    <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Note for Developers:</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/80">
                            Configure your environment with <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">laravelgpt.local</span> domain for testing secured endpoints.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- CTA buttons -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-2">
                        <a href="https://laravelgpt.com" class="btn-primary text-center py-3.5 px-8">
                            Get Started
                            <span class="text-sm block opacity-90">Explore Laravel GPT</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://laravelgpt.com/docs" class="btn-secondary text-center py-3.5 px-8">
                            View Documentation
                            <span class="text-sm block opacity-90">Integration guide available</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Product showcase image -->
                <div class="w-full md:w-[40%] relative">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#1A0033] to-transparent md:hidden z-10"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-0 h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-purple-400/20 rounded-xl blur-lg"></div>
                            <img
                                    src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laravelcompany/laravelcompany.com/refs/heads/main/public/logo-light.svg"
                                    alt="Laravel GPT Dashboard"
                                    class="relative rounded-xl border border-white/20 shadow-xl z-10"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bottom testimonial/quote -->
            <div class="mt-12 bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
                <blockquote class="text-white/90 italic">
                    "Laravel GPT brings AI superpowers to your Laravel apps, making it easier to build smarter, conversational, and more engaging experiences."
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Card>
</Section>
